Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The rat race
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407jfy
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 11 Sep 1977
How to quit the rat race and learn to live within your means. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.